{
  "stem": "14867.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And at that time, of course, most people traveled with a horse and buggy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I approached a-- an old coachman, and I said, will you please take me out of town-- out of town?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, where do you want to go?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I said, out of town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And of course, that was the first time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was an old man-- toothless, ugly, filthy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he says, OK, I'll take you, if you give me-- and he-- he mentioned more than what I had.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I said to myself, I'll deal with him later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As we drive out from [NON-ENGLISH], he release his seat-- you know, the coach in the seat was elevated-- and comes to sit down next to me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And start taking me around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I start getting the chills.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then he start telling me, you know, as we go on-- first, he told me about a few towns where I can go, whatever.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, as we go on, I-- I have a friend who has a little cottage, and he's not there during the day.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why don't you and I try to rest there a little bit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, that's fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's terrific.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as we came, and I said to myself, what am I going to do?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, he's driving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then he comes to this house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he says, he's going to the back to see if the door is open, because usually he left him a key in case he's tired.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyway, he went, and I started to run.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I run.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I didn't stop running.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Did you know where you were?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I ran and I slept.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "During the day, I came to a-- to a town.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
